23 other cells and from the general assets of the protected cell company.
24 (4) Prohibit the assets attributable to a cell from being charged with the
25 liabilities of any other cell or the general liabilities of the protected cell company.
26 (5) Specify the rights and obligations of cell owners with respect to their
27 cells.
